Package com.ideopoly.src

Provides the source files for the Ideopoly game project.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardCell
    A BoardCell represents any of the cells running along the outside edge of the game board.
    BoardPosition
    Class that represents a standing position on the game board.
    CashCell
    Class to represent a player's cash in the GUI.
    Chance
    Class to represent a Chance card.
    ChanceOrCommChestCell
    Represents a Chance or Community Chest cell on the game board.
    CharacterSelect
    Class to represent the character select screen, after the user has decided to start a game.
    CommunityChest
    Represents a card in the Community Chest stack.
    IdeopolyGUI
    Class to contain the GUI of the game board.
    Menu
    Represents the main menu for the game.
    Player
    Class that represents a player.
    PropagandaOutlet
    Class to represent a given propaganda outlet.
    Railroad
    Represents any of the four railroads.
    SpecialCell
    Represents any of the BoardCells that do not easily fall into a specific category.
    TestHelper
    Class to provide helper methods for use in my testing classes.
    UtilityCell
    Represents the common behaviors of the Water Works and Electric Company cells.
